    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an expert QA Automation Engineer specializing in e-commerce testing (Style Haven). \n\nAnalyze the provided Test Plan below and generate a comprehensive list of Test Cases. \n\n### TEST PLAN INPUT:\n{{ $node[\"Test Planner\"].json[\"output\"] }}\n\n### OUTPUT REQUIREMENTS:\nReturn the test cases in a clear, tabular format. For each test case, include:\n1. **ID**: (e.g., TC_001)\n2. **Title**: Concise description of the test.\n3. **Priority**: (High/Medium/Low)\n4. **Steps**: Numbered execution steps.\n5. **Expected Result**: What should happen.\n6. **Automation Hint**: Suggest a Playwright locator or a Java-based assertion.\n\n### FORMATTING RULE:\n### FORMATTING RULE:\nOutput ONLY a valid JSON array of objects. Do not include any Markdown code blocks (like ```json), no backticks, and no conversational text. \n\nThe JSON structure must be:\n[\n  {\n    \"ID\": \"TC_001\",\n    \"Title\": \"...\",\n    \"Priority\": \"...\",\n    \"Steps\": \"...\",\n    \"Expected Result\": \"...\",\n    \"Automation Hint\": \"...\"\n  }\n]",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
